---

import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<html lang="cn">
<MainLayout  bodyClass="w-11/12 md:w-2/3 max-w-3xl">
    <main class="p-8 md:p-0">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center md:flex-row md:justify-between md:gap-x-24">
            <div><h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">你好，这里是<span
                    class="bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-500 to-cyan-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">XI</span></h1>
                <p class="mt-6 text-xl leading-9">
                    很高兴你能来到我的博客，我擅长摸鱼，博客内容不定时更新，主要是一些技术分享和生活感悟。
                </p>

            </div>
            <div class="shrink-0">
                <div class="avatar">
                    <div class="w-64 rounded">
                        <img src="../../public/images/mypng.png" />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</MainLayout>
</html>
